        <Parent_String>reproductions (derivative objects) [300015643], copies (derivative objects) [300015640], derivative objects [300121293], object genres by original and derivative [300235003], object genres (object classifications) [300185712], Object Genres (hierarchy name) [300185711], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
